\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Enacting an overarching federal privacy statue to establish general requirements governing Internet privacy practices of all sectors.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Ensuring that the overseeing agency or agencies have notice-and-comment rulemaking authority to provide clarity, enforcement fairness, and flexibility.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Increasing effectiveness of the overseeing agency by providing authority to impose civil penalties for first-time violations.\cb1 \
